OL,3,CPetting farm fined after disease
OL,4,Cinfects hundreds of visitors
OL,6,FA farm owner on the Isle of Wight has
OL,7,Fbeen fined #8,000 after hundreds of
OL,8,Fpeople visiting her petting farm
OL,9,Fcaught an infectious disease, which
OL,10,Fled to several people being
OL,11,Fhospitalised.
OL,13,FSharon Wheeler, 60, ran a bottle
OL,14,Ffeeding activity at Hazelgrove Farm,
OL,15,Fin Ryde, between April and May 2023,
OL,16,Fwhere visitors could buy a bottle of
OL,17,Fmilk to feed lambs and goat kids.
