OL,3,CPetting farm fined after disease
OL,4,Cinfects hundreds of visitors
OL,6,FFollowing this, around 264 visitors
OL,7,Fwere infected with 'cryptosporidiosis'
OL,8,F- a highly infectious disease caused
OL,9,Fby a parasite.
OL,11,FThe Health Service Executive and UK
OL,12,FHealth Security Agency traced the
OL,13,Foutbreak to when Wheeler ran the
OL,14,Fbottle feeding activity at her farm.
OL,16,FHalf of those infected were children
OL,17,Fand 5% of cases ended up in hospital
OL,18,Fovernight.
