OL,3,CPetting farm fined after disease
OL,4,Cinfects hundreds of visitors
OL,6,FSome victims said they experienced the
OL,7,Fworst diarrhoea and vomiting they had
OL,8,Fever had and were left fearing for
OL,9,Ftheir children's health.
OL,11,FOthers said they had been put off ever
OL,12,Fvisiting a farm again and had
OL,13,Fexperienced lasting psychological
OL,14,Feffects.
OL,16,FRegulators found several failings at
OL,17,Fthe site, from failing to control
OL,18,Fvisitors' contact with animals, to not
OL,19,Fproperly warning people of the
OL,20,Factivity's risks.
