OL,6,FAt a hearing at Southampton
OL,7,FMagistrates' court, Wheeler pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to breaching the Health and
OL,9,FSafety at Work Act and was ordered to
OL,10,Fpay a fine, as well as costs of
OL,11,F#9,528.35.
OL,13,FDrawing on victims' statements,
OL,14,FDistrict Judge Galloway said: "There
OL,15,Fis no doubt that the events to which
OL,16,Fthey refer are and were serious".
OL,18,FHe highlighted the long "psychological
OL,19,Ftoll experienced and PTSD" they
OL,20,Fexperienced, given "the fact that the
OL,21,Fillness was life-threatening."
