OL,6,FCryptosporidiosis is a form of
OL,7,Fzoonotic disease caused by the
OL,8,Fparasite, cryptosporidium. The disease
OL,9,Faffects humans and some animals,
OL,10,Fparticularly those on farms, and its
OL,11,Fsymptoms include abdominal cramps,
OL,12,Fdiarrhoea, and nausea.
OL,14,FOnly a small number of the parasites
OL,15,Fare required to make someone ill and
OL,16,Fthey can survive in an environment for
OL,17,Fa significant amount of time.
