OL,6,F"If the zoonotic risks had been
OL,7,Fproperly controlled this incident
OL,8,Fcould have been avoided, but the
OL,9,Ffailures during the animal feeding
OL,10,Factivity meant a large number of
OL,11,Fvisitors became ill and some suffered
OL,12,Flasting effects.
OL,14,F"As with most activities, visits to
OL,15,Ffarms and farm attractions can never
OL,16,Fbe considered free from risk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
