OL,6,F"However, it is possible to reduce the
OL,7,Flevels of risk by implementing control
OL,8,Fmeasures and safe practices to ensure
OL,9,Fthat workers and members of the public
OL,10,Fare not put at risk and still provide
OL,11,Fa valuable and enjoyable recreational
OL,12,Fand educational experience."
OL,14,FThe HSE found adults affected by the
OL,15,Foutbreak had to take time off work and
OL,16,Fschool, amounting to 1,254 lost days.
